<p>
	Shades of Autumn is a Tales of Avalon fairy designed by Lisa Parker. This fairy is made from resin and finished with beautiful colours. The fairy is lying on fallen leaves with one hand under her chin and the other on the leaves. Her legs are bent upwards and crossed at the ankles. She looks like she is just watching the world go by and enjoying nature. She is created with warm autumnal colours that look fantastic together and complement every part of this fairy. She has a beautiful expression on her face and her fantastic wings are closed on her back as she relaxes. This fairy comes packaged in a decorative gift box making her a perfect gift for a fairy lover. She measures 17cm long, 15cm tall and 9cm wide.</p>
